OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrans prisoners to be      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fplaced based on birth      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fgender                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Newly convicted or remanded transgender
OL,6, prison inmates will initially be placed
OL,7, in jails according to their gender at  
OL,8, birth, the Scottish Prison Service     
OL,9, (SPS) has confirmed.                   
OL,11,FThe policy was confirmed in an urgent  
OL,12,Freview which found a double rapist     
OL,13,Fbeing placed in a women's jail did not 
OL,14,Fput female prisoners at risk of harm.  
OL,16,FHowever, the SPS said it received      
OL,17,F"conflicting" details on Isla Bryson.  
OL,19,FIt also called for an urgent review of 
OL,20,Fadmission rules for some inmates.      
